{"tid":1393204,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［疑似騙局］1977股東快去報案","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T04:41:40.000Z","uid":189698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe244af5a9846d959232037d6fd0d3e046050ac","tid":1393204,"uid":189698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"安樂工程(<a href=\"http://1977.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1977.HK&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl53Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=c8bb4095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1977.HK</a>) 上市20日即發盈警，應該創咗香港記錄。我又唔信招股期間管理層／保薦人唔知公司財政有問題囉，證監會一定要追究。另外有邊個抽咗IPO嘅可以去報警及向證監會投訴，懷疑墮入投資騙局，切勿姑息匪徒，一定要將騙徒繩之於法，保持香港投資市場聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n報警請打999 (請注明懷疑被安樂工程及交銀國際投資銀行部詐騙)<br />\n<br />\n向證監會投訴: <a href=\"https://www.sfc.hk/web/TC/lodge-a-complaint/against-intermediaries-and-market-activities.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfc.hk%2Fweb%2FTC%2Flodge-a-complaint%2Fagainst-intermediaries-and-market-activities.html&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl53Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=f3fd6796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sfc.hk/web/TC/lodge-a-complaint/against-intermediaries-and-market-activities.html</a><br />\n<br />\n安樂工程(<a href=\"http://1977.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1977.HK&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl53Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=c8bb4095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1977.HK</a>)現報 $1.07，跌穿招股價，創上市新低。<br />\n<br />\n#安樂工程 #一股不買 #全城杯葛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gHt1UP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gHt1UP.png&h=e690b49f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6df36faab5b2911aaf13ea8c545c5a1a217f71c9","tid":1393204,"uid":189698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"證監會必須回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8646af58fb0c12d5bd07213c8d7e5f7fe7573dd3","tid":1393204,"uid":2442,"like":2,"dislike